  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Family
    This class is an extension of the previously implemented Passenger class and just like Group, it has at least 2 members.
    Group
    This class is an extension of the previously implemented Passenger class, but unlike Single, it has at least 2 members.
    MainFile  
    Member
    Contains information about a single passenger or a member of a group / family.
    NecesaryPriorityQueue
    This class contains a heap (represented as an array), a size variable, which represents the number of elements in the heap and a writer to print the priority queue in a given file.
    Passenger
    This is our main Passenger / Pasager class, the one which will be used to implement the heap / priority queue.
    Single
    This class is an extension of the previously implemented Passenger class, which has only 1 member.
    Ticket
    Contains information about flight tickets: 1) the ticket type
    2) if a passenger has prioritary embarking with his/her ticket
    3) if the respective passenger has special needs
